## What?
openframeworks.cc - unofficial (pre-release) - Development-Bundle

..mostly for tinkering with openframeworks at it's early release stage.

## platforms

  - Mac OSX (xcode)
  - Windows (codeblocks)
  - Linux (codeblocks)

## openFrameworks subversion gets merged frequently into this bundle.



## usage/install

  before using this bundle make sure to follow the setup-
  guide according to your running operation system!

  ## Mac Xcode
	
  - install git
      "port install git-core +svn"
  - install Xcode
      "http://developer.apple.com/TOOLS/xcode/"
	
  ## Windows Codeblocks
	
  - install git
      "http://code.google.com/p/msysgit/"
  - install quicktime
      "http://www.apple.com/de/quicktime/download/"
  - install codeblocks
      "http://www.openframeworks.cc/setup/codeblocks_setup_guide"

	
  ## Linux Codeblocks - Debian (lenny)
	
  - install debian with installer
      "debian-Lenny-DI-rc2-i386-businesscard.iso"
		
  - install build-essential, git and xfce4
      "apt-get install screen sudo build-essential subversion"
      "apt-get install git-core git-svn xorg xfce4 mesa-utils"

  - install codeblocks, and dependencies
      "apt-get install gdb libwxgtk2.8-0 libwxgtk2.8-dev wx2.8-headers wx-common"
      "wget http://mesh.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/codeblocks/codeblocks-8.02debian-i386.tar.gz"
      "tar -zxf codeblocks-8.02debian-i386.tar.gz -c codeblocks_install"
      "dpkg -i codeblocks_install/lib*.deb"
      "dpkg -i codeblocks_install/codeblocks*.deb"

  - install openframeworks dependencies for codeblocks
      "apt-get install zlib1g-dev libpoco5-dev libasound2-dev libraw1394-dev"
      "apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev libxmu-dev libxxf86vm-dev"

